<p><ent>Earn</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Earn
<hw>Earn</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See 4th <er>Yearn</er>.]</ety>
<def>To long; to yearn.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And ever as he rode, his heart did <qex>earn</qex>⟦br⟧
To prove his puissance in battle brave.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Earn</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 5 ====
HEADWORD: Earn
<hw>Earn</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>irnan</ets> to run.
⟦root⟧11. See <er>Rennet</er>, and cf. <er>Yearnings</er>.]</ety>
<def>To curdle, as milk.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>earned</ent>⟦br⟧
